pageContext.claim: “You know talking about the fake media. I was doing that speech recently and I said and each one of them gets a free Rolls Royce. And so the media, one of the particular groups, you know. They said, he said they get a Rolls Royce but they don't get a Rolls Royce. They said that. They don't get a Rolls Royce. They said he gets a Pinocchio for that.”
pageContext.analysis: Actually, the Pinocchios were for his claim that Democrats wanted to give immigrant driver's licenses. We noted that he later said he was joking about the luxury cars.
